{
  "chapter": 9,
  "chapter_summary": "第九回　武当之行：本章围绕主要人物的遭遇、江湖见闻与冲突推进展开。第九回武当之行两人略为将息，便辞别了常漫天夫妇，赶往武当山上去。武当山本是楚北最有名的一处山峦，山属巴山支脉，周围八百多里，有三十六悬岩，二十七高峰。最高之处，名天柱峰，那就是真武修炼之地。此外还有南岩、五龙峰、紫霄峰、展旗峰等，都是道家清修之处。高峰白云深处，三两苍鹰在低低盘旋着，地上的野兔，急剧地在野草丛中飞奔，清风扑鼻，晨露迎面，章节中人物往来、言语试探和武林局势互相交织，为后续恩怨、师承与行动埋下线索。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那不是吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 20,
      "line_end": 20
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来两位施主是来找护法的四位师叔的。不过……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 32
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这个贫道倒不敢做主。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 38,
      "line_end": 38
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "四仪剑客难道全出去了吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "出家人不打诳语。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "若是十分重要的事，跟贫道说也一样。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 58,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "四仪剑客既不在，就请道长们带在下去参拜妙一真人，在下……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_wei_ming",
      "speaker_name": "尚未明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "要怎样才能见得？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 68,
      "line_end": 68
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_wei_ming",
      "speaker_name": "尚未明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好一个出家人，一开口说话，却像强盗一样。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "师兄们也是太不小心了，让这样个小姑娘将武当山看做无人之境，日后传出江湖，岂不是个笑话！",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 132
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这事若要告诉熊倜，他岂非要笑我武当派无用？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 139,
      "line_end": 139
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他倒晓得我的姓名了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 203,
      "line_end": 203
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "玄真观",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 221,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "贫僧去回禀家师一声，两位在此稍候。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 239,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "家师请两位进去。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 241,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_wei_ming",
      "speaker_name": "尚未明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "请进。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 249,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "家师已仙去了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 285,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你深致歉意，又有何用。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 337,
      "line_end": 337
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大哥，这是不是就是天阴教？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 359,
      "line_end": 359
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_wei_ming",
      "speaker_name": "尚未明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "天阴教？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 365,
      "line_end": 365
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "果然来了。恐怕夺剑之人，就是此人。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 381,
      "line_end": 381
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 383,
      "line_end": 383
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "果然就是这个小子夺的剑。",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 431,
      "line_end": 431
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_wei_ming",
      "speaker_name": "尚未明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这位敢情就是名传四海的天阴教焦教主了。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 499,
      "line_end": 499
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不敢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 501,
      "line_end": 501
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朋友说话可要放清楚些。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 525,
      "line_end": 525
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_wei_ming",
      "speaker_name": "尚未明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "兄弟倒想说清楚些，只怕说清楚了，阁下……",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 527,
      "line_end": 527
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "那么你倒是快说呀。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 594,
      "line_end": 594
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这位天阴教主看起人来，可真让人吃不消。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 600,
      "line_end": 600
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "教主说得好，兄弟和贵教总算同处两河，教主若能赏兄弟一个面子……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 636,
      "line_end": 636
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只怕没有那么容易。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 670,
      "line_end": 670
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就凭着这些人，就想能拦得住我吗？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 680,
      "line_end": 680
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "试试看。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 682,
      "line_end": 682
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "教主——",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 694,
      "line_end": 694
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiong_ti",
      "speaker_name": "熊倜",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "且慢。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 698,
      "line_end": 698
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不错，不错，果然出落得一表人材。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 704,
      "line_end": 704
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_wei_ming",
      "speaker_name": "尚未明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "原来她在对敌动手时都会笑的。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 726,
      "line_end": 726
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "正是，正是，大家都该下山了。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 780,
      "line_end": 780
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_wei_ming",
      "speaker_name": "尚未明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "且慢。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 782,
      "line_end": 782
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是呀，这武当山岂是任人来去的地方。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 792,
      "line_end": 792
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_wei_ming_ubeyp_ubupt_ubtee",
      "speaker_name": "尚未明冷笑着",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "武当山当然不是任人来去的地方。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 794,
      "line_end": 794
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "阁下此话何意？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 798,
      "line_end": 798
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "唷，又有谁在武当山上抢了东西呀？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 800,
      "line_end": 800
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就是阁下。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 804,
      "line_end": 804
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朋友说话可要放清楚些。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 806,
      "line_end": 806
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_wei_ming",
      "speaker_name": "尚未明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "堂堂天阴教主，做事又何必推三诿四？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 808,
      "line_end": 808
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ubfdm_ubeax_uccud_ubdpk_wei",
      "speaker_name": "制住那两位",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "话声一顿，又冷笑道：",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 812,
      "line_end": 812
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "道长何以见得我在贵处伤人夺剑，难道有人看到了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 820,
      "line_end": 820
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "贯日剑？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 826,
      "line_end": 826
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "贯日剑，哈，哈，原来这柄是贯日剑。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 828,
      "line_end": 828
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "阁下这柄剑叫什么名字？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 834,
      "line_end": 834
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是江湖上传闻多年的'倚天剑'。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 836,
      "line_end": 836
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你干什么？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 840,
      "line_end": 840
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_ubiyn_ran",
      "speaker_name": "居然",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你……",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 846,
      "line_end": 846
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "出家人焉能谎语。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 866,
      "line_end": 866
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "施主们自去无妨，只是敝教这两个……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 924,
      "line_end": 924
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "此间事既已了……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 930,
      "line_end": 930
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_wei_ming",
      "speaker_name": "尚未明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只怕此间事还未了。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 932,
      "line_end": 932
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "小兄弟，还有什么事？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 934,
      "line_end": 934
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_shang_wei_ming",
      "speaker_name": "尚未明",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下也正有此意。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 956,
      "line_end": 956
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "说不得只有如此了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 1024,
      "line_end": 1024
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_yun",
      "speaker_name": "夏芸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老爷子不要怕，我只是来讨碗豆浆喝的。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 1092,
      "line_end": 1092
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_yun",
      "speaker_name": "夏芸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这女的好美。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 1136,
      "line_end": 1136
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "朋友——",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 1144,
      "line_end": 1144
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "大王——",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 1150,
      "line_end": 1150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_yun",
      "speaker_name": "夏芸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "他们大概不知道我身怀武功，是以才会有这种表情。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 1162,
      "line_end": 1162
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我真倒霉，一出手便碰到这种人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 1176,
      "line_end": 1176
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你真的想拦路劫财？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 1180,
      "line_end": 1180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_yun",
      "speaker_name": "夏芸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你试试看。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 1188,
      "line_end": 1188
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你开始数吧。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 1200,
      "line_end": 1200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_yun_ubjzk_ubftz_ubfuh",
      "speaker_name": "夏芸开口叫",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 1206,
      "line_end": 1206
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这个小姑娘到底怎么回事？",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 1240,
      "line_end": 1240
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "停下来。",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 1286,
      "line_end": 1286
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这个道士两只眼睛看起人来贼兮兮的，一定不是好人，我真想教训教训他……",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 1294,
      "line_end": 1294
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "难道她也认得熊倜？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 1412,
      "line_end": 1412
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_yun",
      "speaker_name": "夏芸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你也认得倜……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 1424,
      "line_end": 1424
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是呀，我也认得你的倜哥哥。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 1426,
      "line_end": 1426
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_yun",
      "speaker_name": "夏芸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "怎么我的心事老是被她说中呢！",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 1442,
      "line_end": 1442
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_man_tian",
      "speaker_name": "常漫天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姑娘是不是想找熊老弟？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 1444,
      "line_end": 1444
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "不过你可得先将这两匹马弄好。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 1454,
      "line_end": 1454
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_yun",
      "speaker_name": "夏芸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我家在关外有个马场……",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 1466,
      "line_end": 1466
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这怎么办，这怎么办？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 1500,
      "line_end": 1500
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "常大哥。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 1520,
      "line_end": 1520
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_man_tian",
      "speaker_name": "常漫天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "呀，果然是你。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 1522,
      "line_end": 1522
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chang_man_tian",
      "speaker_name": "常漫天",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "老弟，你来晚了一步。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 1540,
      "line_end": 1540
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你有什么办法？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 1558,
      "line_end": 1558
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_yun",
      "speaker_name": "夏芸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这人竟认得我？",
      "tone": "厉声",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 1628,
      "line_end": 1628
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姑娘难道要找他？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 1660,
      "line_end": 1660
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_yun",
      "speaker_name": "夏芸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "是呀，我们都在找他。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 1662,
      "line_end": 1662
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_hao",
      "speaker_name": "边浩",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姑娘不是一个人吗？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 1664,
      "line_end": 1664
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_yun",
      "speaker_name": "夏芸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "还有人在后面。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 1666,
      "line_end": 1666
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_hao",
      "speaker_name": "边浩",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姑娘要找熊兄弟，碰到我是再好没有了……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 1668,
      "line_end": 1668
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_yun",
      "speaker_name": "夏芸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你知道他在哪里？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 1670,
      "line_end": 1670
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_hao",
      "speaker_name": "边浩",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姑娘许久不见，却越来越漂亮了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 1682,
      "line_end": 1682
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xia_yun",
      "speaker_name": "夏芸",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "喂，倜哥哥到底在哪里，你倒是快说呀。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 1684,
      "line_end": 1684
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bian_hao",
      "speaker_name": "边浩",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "姑娘倒真性急得紧。",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 1686,
      "line_end": 1686
    },
    {
      "speaker": null,
      "speaker_name": "未明说话人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "熊——熊大哥此刻——此刻他只怕已——",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 9,
      "line_start": 1702,
